        "height": 440,
        "content": "## ‚¨áÔ∏è **4. Download pdf**\n- **Purpose:** Download the pdffile.  \n- **Functionality:** Uses the media URL from the previous API response to download the pdf file.  \n- **Output:** Stores the raw pdf binary for upload.\n\n-"
