        "height": 400,
        "content": "## ‚òÅÔ∏è **5. Upload To Google Drive**\n- **Purpose:** Store pdfin Google Drive.  \n- **Functionality:** Uploads the downloaded pdf into the specified Drive folder.  \n- **Output:** Returns a file ID for the uploaded file.\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "e55bf6b2-69ff-4454-a27c-6e758dd16835",
