        "content": "## üîë **6. Google Drive Set Permission**\n- **Purpose:** Make the file publicly accessible.  \n- **Functionality:** Sets file permissions to `Anyone with the link can view`.  \n- **Output:** Provides a sharable `webViewLink`.\n"
